{"tid":1836170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察幾時義務到中國協助防疫工作","createTime":"2020-01-23T06:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T10:18:38.000Z","uid":57588,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6fbd1c00ec8904f6b513021832efa990543171","tid":1836170,"uid":57588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"見到中國爆發疫症真係好心痛<br />\n眼見依幾個月解放軍義務係香港止暴製亂<br />\n而且中國人民都一直咁支持人民英雄香港警察<br />\n所以，我呼籲香港警察係中國依個咁重要既時刻<br />\n派遣二千名警察前往武漢以協助防疫工作<br />\n向全中國全世界發揮你地勇毅既精神<br />\n加上警方一直受專業訓練，以及先進既設備<br />\n對於隔離工作一定好有用<br />\n只要香港警察同解放軍合作<br />\n中國人一定好感動<br />\n<br />\n中國人咁支持香港警察<br />\n香港警察時時候報因了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gm2CyF1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGm2CyF1.png&h=1c830b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿Sir 我支持你</span>"},{"pid":"5b1ec32013236bf782047ae5ef1f58037d99c44e","tid":1836170,"uid":75311,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:19:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">毛賊神經病就有, 佢地就快智障</span></span>"},{"pid":"f26b2868837730b9c640153dd9e1b4cbd5193a62","tid":1836170,"uid":88133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b1ec32013236bf782047ae5ef1f58037d99c44e","tid":1836170,"uid":75311,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:19:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">毛賊神經病就有, 佢地就快智障</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:20:51.000Z","msg":"旺角預言家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040928602e3f655d67e36b848476fbf0a069d328","tid":1836170,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_191022/20191022_68d3d63b4d680cce6760d8SZ2u3NJ5wm.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"ddfb6d263ec97fca9e6569624a3e687b914088ef